text.en_US: To jump around that block you need a little bit of help.
Inch yourself off the bottom of the ledge until it pulls you back from falling off.
Then all you do is hold straight right to clear the corner without losing momentum!
Just make sure you do not press an upward direction before you have fully passed by the block.
There are multiple ways around this jump.
The easiest way should be to do a corner jump like you just did and do a single dash long jump upwards.
Just try to keep holding up when you land on the ice pillar.
